    "\"), in particular, demonstrates superior efficacy, reducing the ASR of PAPs on GPT-4 from 92% to 2%, signifying a notable enhancement in practical post-hoc defense.",
    "More interestingly, adaptive defenses, initially tailored for PAPs, are also effective against other types of adversarial prompts.",
    "For instance, adjusting the system prompt to emphasize resistance to persuasion, we witnessed a decline in the ASR for the GCG from 86% to 0% on GPT-3.5.",
